        public java.lang.String composite(java.lang.String formatKey,
                                  java.lang.String joiner,
                                  java.lang.Object objectToInvokeMethodOn)
        A property that is composed of other properties. It firstly fetches the formatKey using fetch(String). It will proceed to convert the returned properties from the fetch(String) method to a methodName and invoke this method against the object passed in. Finally, concatenation occurs with the return values of the methods using the joiner parameter as a separator.
